testsuite.name: application.JoinChatUseCaseTest

testcase.name: should not join the channel if the user is already in the channel()
should join the channel and create the channel if the user has previously logged in and the channel did not exist()
should set activeChat room to the latest joined channel()
should not allow to join the channel and not create it if chatRoomName is empty()
should not join the channel if the channel is full()
should not join the channel if the user is not logged in()
should join the channel if the user has previously logged in and the channel existed()
